Available Tools: share_file | set_permissions | get_shared_link | revoke_access | list_collaborators
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "file_id": "string", "user_email": "string", "permission": "view|comment|edit", "expires_at": "string" }
Response Schema: { "file_id": "string", "shared_link": "string", "collaborators": [{ "email": "string", "permission": "string" }] }
---
Question: Revoke access for alex.miller@techcorp.com on the Q3 budget spreadsheet and show me who still has access.
Call: { "func_call": "revoke_access", "file_id": "file_8923_budget_q3", "user_email": "alex.miller@techcorp.com", "permission": "edit", "expires_at": "" }
Response: { "file_id": "file_8923_budget_q3", "shared_link": "https://storage.example.com/s/x9z2a1", "collaborators": [{ "email": "sarah.jones@techcorp.com", "permission": "edit" }, { "email": "mike.chen@techcorp.com", "permission": "view" }] }

